## Auth

- `authMiddleware` sets `req.user` from JWT
- Socket auth: token in `socket.handshake.auth.token`, verified in `io.use()`

## Redis (Upstash)

- URL: `rediss://` (TLS) вЂ” use ioredis, not the `redis` package
- `setUserOnline` / `setUserOffline` manage presence + DB `isOnline` flag
- Client emits `presence:ping` every 25s to keep TTL alive

## Rate Limiting

- `generalLimiter` commented out in `index.ts` (dev)
- `authLimiter`, `otpLimiter`, `uploadLimiter` in `middleware/rateLimit.ts`
